OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and occasional clear spells this
OL,7,Fevening, with some patchy mist, fog or
OL,8,Flow cloud developing in a few places.
OL,9,FWinds remaining light. Feeling cooler.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FBright or sunny spells but
OL,12,Fturning cloudier for a time later as
OL,13,Fscattered showers move south, with a
OL,14,Fcooler northerly breeze developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
